wiki.content:
"3's & 7's" is the second single by Queens of the Stone Age from their 2007 album Era Vulgaris. It was released on June 4, 2007 and followed the digital download-only "Sick, Sick, Sick". The single has debuted at number one on the United Kingdom rock chart and at number nineteen on the official UK top 40 singles chart.
